  .moved h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h2); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight); margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm); }
  .moved p { font-family: var(--font-body); color: var(--text); }
  .moved a { font-weight: var(--fw-semibold); }
</style>
<div class="container moved">
  <span class="eyebrow">Moved</span>
  <h1>Songs That Found Me at the Right Time has a new home</h1>
  <p>This series now lives at <a href="/sessions/">/sessions/</a>. Redirecting you there now.</p>
</div>
